data.description: Motivated seller bring your offers. Beautifully located, priced to sell home is located in a tranquil desert setting with clear sky's of mountain views. This 3 bed 2 bath homestead comes equipped with a private well, storage shed, chicken coop, and unfinished root cellar. It's perfect with modern touches: updated flooring and energy updates to save money on utilities. Close access to Interstate 10 with Phoenix metro just a short drive away. Your Arizona ranch is situated on a corner lot that is over an acre. Make an offer today on this gorgeous property and make your dreams of a peaceful life come true.
